title: Made As Intended Gemstone Bracelets Trio - Jasper, Pyrite and Onyx
features: 8MM Zebra Jasper Beads with 4MM Antique Sterling Silver Rondelles and Antique Om
6MM Pyrite Beads with 2.5MM Sterling Silver Rounds and 6MM Pewter Eye bead
6MM Matte Onyx and a 8MM Stainless Steel I AM bead
Regular size fits up to 7" wrist. Strung on stretchable nylon.
description: Our Trio for Health and Strength was intentionally designed with your personal strength and vitality in mind. Zebra Jasper is said to impart determination to all tasks, to bring you strength to overcome obstacles and encourages you to be honest with yourself. Pyrite supports the ideal of perfect health and well-being, drawing on universal energies to activate the nourishing energies of the body. Named for the Greek word for fire – it is said to protect our inner fire and Vitality. And how we love Onyx – thought to be one of the strongest stones of protection and grounding, Onyx is said to help you develop both physical and emotional strength, retaining energy rather than allowing it dissipate, enabling one to build up vigor and vitality, stamina, and focus. Our jewelry is handmade with intention and love.
